  "detailed_description": "A huge crisis broke out in the Mirror-verse. In the name of justice (or probably mischief), the bishojos went to war! Select your heroine and fight! The mini-game collection of Mirror-verse: Mirror Party<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[GAMPLAY]</h2>There are currently 4 minigames, we plan to add as many as we can before the formal release.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/84ecead6ea46c9637e8fed6c544818e5.poster.avif?t=1755198468\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/84ecead6ea46c9637e8fed6c544818e5.webm?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/84ecead6ea46c9637e8fed6c544818e5.mp4?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><li>Tank Battlefield: No one can stop a trumping tank! Except for another tank. Wipe your opponents off of this earth, and earn some points along the way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/61e13e26da898c99a6d16046210e7b08.poster.avif?t=1755198468\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/61e13e26da898c99a6d16046210e7b08.webm?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/61e13e26da898c99a6d16046210e7b08.mp4?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Leah's Secret Room: Leah has lost many of her stuff and she needs your help to find it. And of course, she's going to reward you... in her own way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/a4616f3790484660293d15f731957692.poster.avif?t=1755198468\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/a4616f3790484660293d15f731957692.webm?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/a4616f3790484660293d15f731957692.mp4?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Fireball Royale: Launch your mighty fireballs at your rivals and see what happens! Be careful of those poisonous fog, lightning, and more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/ef5e85dda7d7d1af497c8fb845646557.poster.avif?t=1755198468\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/ef5e85dda7d7d1af497c8fb845646557.webm?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/ef5e85dda7d7d1af497c8fb845646557.mp4?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Frenzy Farm: Who can resist the cute animals? But how about when they have gone frenzy! Contain them with the pumpkins!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[GACHA MACHINE]</h2>Getting a little tired? I bet our 300+ collectibles can get you back. See those Gacha Tokens you got, put them in the Gacha Machine, and collect as many as you can. 100+ CGs, 100+ Cosplay Albums, Avatars for the Launcher, OST theme songs of Mirror Series.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/35f890c852854dea172c6c7014ffa050.poster.avif?t=1755198468\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/35f890c852854dea172c6c7014ffa050.webm?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/35f890c852854dea172c6c7014ffa050.mp4?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>We plan to increase the number of collectibles from 300 to 1000 before the formal release.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[FEATURE]</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3D-Chibi rendition of characters from the Mirror Series.<br><br></li><li>Covered many genres of games of interesting mechanics.<br><br></li><li>Over 300 (1000 before the formal release) collectibles from the Gacha Machine.<br><br></li><li>On-line component, more people, more fun!</li></ul>",
